Class AbstractRoleEntity.Builder

  • Object
    • buri.ddmsence.AbstractRoleEntity.Builder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBuilder, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:

    Enclosing class:
    AbstractRoleEntity

    public abstract static class AbstractRoleEntity.Builder
extends Object
implements IBuilder, Serializable
    Abstract Builder for this DDMS component.

    Builders which are based upon this abstract class should implement the commit() method, returning the appropriate concrete object type.
